Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配备着以电脑为导航系统的赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“CYBER F0RMULA”正式登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代替“F-l”的2l世纪赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令全世界人都狂热起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,!Effect,新世纪GPX “CYBER F0RMULA”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.82,0:00:33.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快快出发 不用有任何担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮助你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.70,0:00:43.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思议的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.25,0:00:46.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来自你求助的讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.02,0:00:53.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从昨夜开始一直感觉得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.37,0:00:59.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突如其来的风暴阻挡了前进的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.92,0:01:02.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿望便浮现在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.04,0:01:08.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是喜欢 是奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.10,0:01:14.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都会放在心上 不论什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.56,0:01:19.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的波浪会紧随而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.16,0:01:27.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在马上出发 决不动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.19,0:01:33.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了实现梦想 永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.13,0:01:36.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.34,0:01:43.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快快出发 不用有任何担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.14,0:01:49.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮助你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在隼人跟大友退场以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.35,0:02:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新条直辉辉跟加贺分别得到冠军和亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在场的观众对他们抱以热烈的掌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.39,0:02:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在得到冠军的新条直辉站上颁奖台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直辉伸手向观众们致意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是第八回合以来他得到第二个冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原先的积分再加上这一次的冠军拿到九分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的排名现在已经挤到第二名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.47,0:02:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟排名第一的兰度只差一分而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十场比赛只剩下最后一回合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本冠军杯比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,预计这可能是退场的隼人跟兰度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及直辉这三个人的大混战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.74,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十五话 伤痕累累的赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监督先生 请问大友的伤势怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没可能赶上第十回合的日本冠军赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们以后再来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在没时间回答你们的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.81,0:03:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监督先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的比赛太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友的伤势怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有生命危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚才开始动紧急手术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.72,0:03:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你跟我一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监督先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友选手出事的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是之前跟你冲撞的缘故吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人说大友选手的巴托朗602号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.57,0:03:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为跟你的冲撞之后才会发生故障的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是这个样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事情跟隼人完全无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们马上离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在跟你的车子相撞之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴托朗其实没有受到什么损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车盘的情况怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到处都有裂缝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不把整个底盘拆开来检查的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在是很难判断的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照情况来看 必须要换掉不少的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有问题的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距离第十回合比赛整整还有八天时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有零件的话 开夜车也不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都可以想办法修理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题就在于你说的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超级阿斯拉达是隼人的父亲亲手做的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎跟启动马达都是营生厂制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是像其他的一些小零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些都是隼人的父亲自己亲手制造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就没有第二套零件可以装上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然今天不能参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是隼人的总积分是三十四分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排名还是第三名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在最后一回合拿到冠军的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为世界冠军就不是梦想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然风见留给我们的零件都用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.87,0:05:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还是可以联络老板在日本的工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照原来的尺寸重新制造就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.17,0:05:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总而言之 我们还是要尽己所能的去修理它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 你那边查得怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想阿斯拉应该是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了在撞击中保护程式而切断自己的回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人在比赛之后所说的那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在是很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看样子有必要再检查一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,程式到底是不是真的出了什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,软件的问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那拜托你赶快查明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也赶快开始动作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.20,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么…为什么会变成这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人说大友选手的巴托朗602号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为跟你冲撞之后才会发生故障的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是内圈 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来不及了 我要直接冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 赶快减速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友出事的原因就是那次车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以大友他才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是阿斯拉的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被迫退出比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友出车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你也刚刚才比完赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定很累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这么样关心大友我很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是时间已经不早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是快回去休息比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手术到现在已经八个小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信大友的生命力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的事情就包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.98,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手术很成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就看他自己的体力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.11,0:07:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友 振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…换档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.95,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没有…看到格子旗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友他现在还在战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正朝着终点的格子旗奔走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终点还没到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.91,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像是睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等待赛车手生还是车队工作人员的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在可以回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为庆功宴的关系耽误了时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友他的情况怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手术是已经成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…他到现在还没有恢复意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 那么大友他胜利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对一个赛车手而言 唯一的败北就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他经过了那么大的事故还活了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么他就是胜利了你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不相信这一套呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟大友两个人都输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你冷静一点 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是在激动什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本就不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.87,0:09:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我被阿斯拉背叛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被阿斯拉背叛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息也是赛车手的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茶壶在叫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人除了自己的事故之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像非常在意大友的伤势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为闪电系统的进步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在闪电霹雳车赛中死亡的事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经减少很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只要是赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就一定会有死亡的阴影存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是不变的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有超越那个阴影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇敢战斗下去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才称得上是赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望隼人他也是这么勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对一个十四岁的少年而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许要求太高了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人他一定可以办到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信他可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.99,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么晚才回来也不跟大家连络一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介…你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干什么…我在修阿斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样的东西 根本就没修理的必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.18,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为阿斯拉达的关系而使得大友他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要做傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我 伸介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是它 都是它害了大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你已经很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后我再不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟阿斯拉达一起赛车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.11,0:11:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.25,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.88,0:11:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面开始是直线道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么直线道路 到底在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左转弯 请减速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿过左转弯之后是直线道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的话我能够相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会再相信你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安 隼人 昨晚睡得还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了一杯综合果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喝喝看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.79,0:12:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.93,0:12:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是又在怀疑我的手艺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天大家喝了都说很好喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很啰嗦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我让你看一点东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我利用电脑分析阿斯拉的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模拟了昨天车祸的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天巴托朗在这个地方摇摆不定开到外车道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为大友他注意到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把内车道让给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…没有多久他又回到了你的进路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你相撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个只要用推进器就能够躲过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是当时阿斯拉它却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的那个方法我也模拟过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个地方用推进器加快速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电脑预测如果加快速度的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两辆车的受损程度绝对比现在大的多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果运气不好的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至可能使两位车手同时都丧失性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是应该还有其他的方式可以闪躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比方像是切断引擎使用旋转风扇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他为什么不这么做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少无理取闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达友不是神 它也有无法躲避的事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.18,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 我们的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是让阿斯拉在最佳状态下来帮助你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说你不相信我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不相信我们为你整备的阿斯拉达吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在是忍不住脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实也不是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是为了整理那个资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚你一定熬夜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我这个人除了电脑以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没有什么其他的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望隼人能早点了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我个人是相信隼人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果伸介说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.04,0:15:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个车祸…是大友自己…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早日康复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来啦 事情办得怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天搭乘三点的飞机离开德国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天早上出去后 就一直没回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比赛难免会发生事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.59,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车道的特别状况或者是车手判断太慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何一点小事都可能成为车祸的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…这是没有人能够责备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这一点我想隼人他自己也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.54,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人太关心大友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使他不得不找个对象来责备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他才怪罪阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人他真是太善良了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只靠这样是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是拥有善良…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为隼人是个赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来是闪电霹雳车的话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的世界冠军杯第九回合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生车祸的大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.97,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据说已经恢复了意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过八个小时漫长的手术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于奇迹般的生还了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是根据医师的诊断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友选手今后可能没办法再重返赛车界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于大友选手这样突然的引退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关心他的人都掩不住讶异的神色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他再也不能回来赛车界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太残酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,异常保护系统解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,检查各部份的毁损情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车体的毁损率是百分之九十三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.42,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闪电系统方面没有受到任何的损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前正常运作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,程式检查完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的气温是摄氏九度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样睡着的话 得感冒的可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要破坏我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以后…再也不跟你合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请告诉我你的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为你…因为你的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友的赛车手生命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有办法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友他所发生的车祸跟我没有任何的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用再狡辩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为你…就因为你才会害了大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你很悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感觉到你心中有深沉的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的话非常不合逻辑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.82,0:18:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不知道怎么的 我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有个不合逻辑的程式了解你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心中充满了悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看着这样的你 我也觉得非常的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.07,0:19:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达不只是你一个人的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是我们的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.81,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你却…你却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什么都不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰嗦 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良平 冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我 可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是太令人失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你就不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家是多么的关心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.72,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信你会靠自己的力量重新站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才不去管你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.73,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你就不肯相信我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道…我早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.64,0:20:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那车祸…不是阿斯拉达的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是任何人的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…我不愿意承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要恨一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.29,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我自己懦弱 我懦弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常对不起 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.84,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一切都是因为我的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还把你跟阿斯拉达也牵连了进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以后打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回北海道去开一个牧场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.02,0:21:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然以后我不能再开霹雳车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…我人生的比赛还没有结束呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本冠军杯的时候你一定要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的那一份就拜托你跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他人目光没有在背后注视着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为肩负着使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下双手 仰望天空时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有现在加倍努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能有明天的辉煌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此 不用后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向着自己树立的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎着风前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终我们会是胜利者

